1.title: Urban Gardening
1.plot: Enter a whole new urban jungle, where tropical butterfly pavilions bloom indoors and mini-ecosystems thrive on rooftops.

2.title: Flower Power
2.plot: Did you know you should sanitize a pruner before clipping your rose bush? Get the tips you need to grow your garden right.

3.title: Victory Veggies
3.plot: See how gardening tips used in the WWII effort and practiced by Native American Indians can make your garden grow!

imdb.plot outline: Meet the experts who make the Smithsonian Gardens a stunning living museum year round. See how our horticulturists work tirelessly to overcome urban conditions and freezing temperatures. Learn how all gardeners, from amateur to seasoned, can use their secrets to make their own gardens grow.
